                                </span></span><span data-test="authors-info" class="info__authors"><span><a href="/search?term=Gyubeom%20Hwang&amp;type=author&amp;precise=true&amp;authorlink=true" aria-label="Gyubeom Hwang. Search more articles by this author.">
                                        Gyubeom Hwang<sup>1, 2, 3</sup> <!----></a></span> <span><a aria-label="Visit this author on ORCID website" data-test="orcid-link" target="_blank" href="https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2293-4555"><img src="https://asset.jmir.pub/assets/static/images/Orcid-ID-Logo-Colour.png" alt="Author Orcid Image" aria-label="Author Orcid Image" class="info__orcid-img"></a></span> <span style="margin-left: -2px;">
                                    ;  
