2Fli\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan id=\"ref10\"\u003ECreed TA, Salama L, Slevin R,  et al. Enhancing the quality of cognitive behavioral therapy in community mental health through artificial intelligence generated fidelity feedback (Project AFFECT): a study protocol. BMC Health Serv Res.  Sep 20, 2022;22(1):1177. [\u003Ca target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fdx.doi.org\u002F10.1186\u002Fs12913-022-08519-9\"\u003ECrossRef\u003C\u002Fa\u003E] [\u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov\u002Fentrez\u002Fquery.fcgi?cmd=Retrieve&amp;db=PubMed&amp;list_uids=36127689&amp;dopt=Abstract\" target=\"_blank\"\u003EMedline\u003C\u002Fa\u003E]\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003C\u002Fli\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan id=\"ref11\"\u003EOmar M, Soffer S, Charney AW, Landi I, Nadkarni GN, Klang E. Applications of large language models in psychiatry: a systematic review. Front Psychiatry.   2024;15:1422807. [\u003Ca target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fdx.doi.org\u002F10.3389\u002Ffpsyt.2024.1422807\"\u003ECrossRef\u003C\u002Fa\u003E] [\u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov\u002Fentrez\u002Fquery.fcgi?cmd=Retrieve&amp;db=PubMed&amp;list_uids=38979501&amp;dopt=Abstract\" target=\"_blank\"\u003EMedline\u003C\u002Fa\u003E]\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003C\u002Fli\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan id=\"ref12\"\u003EWang C, Liu S, Yang H, Guo J, Wu Y, Liu J. Ethical considerations of using ChatGPT in health care. J Med Internet Res.  Aug 11, 2023;25:e48009. [\u003Ca target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fdx.doi.org\u002F10.2196\u002F48009\"\u003ECrossRef\u003C\u002Fa\u003E] [\u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov\u002Fentrez\u002Fquery.fcgi?cmd=Retrieve&amp;db=PubMed&amp;list_uids=37566454&amp;dopt=Abstract\" target=\"_blank\"\u003EMedline\u003C\u002Fa\u003E]\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003C\u002Fli\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan id=\"ref13\"\u003EZhang G, Jin Q, Zhou Y,  et al. Closing the gap between open source and commercial large language models for medical evidence summarization. NPJ Digital Med.  Sep 9, 2024;7(1):239. [\u003Ca target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fdx.doi.org\u002F10.1038\u002Fs41746-024-01239-w\"\u003ECrossRef\u003C\u002Fa\u003E] [\u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov\u002Fentrez\u002Fquery.fcgi?cmd=Retrieve&amp;db=PubMed&amp;list_uids=39251804&amp;dopt=Abstract\" target=\"_blank\"\u003EMedline\u003C\u002Fa\u003E]\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003C\u002Fli\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan id=\"ref14\"\u003EFang C, Wu Y, Fu W,  et al. How does ChatGPT-4 preform on non-English national medical licensing examination? An evaluation in Chinese language. PLOS Digital Health.  Dec 2023;2(12):e0000397. [\u003Ca target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fdx.doi.org\u002F10.1371\u002Fjournal.pdig.0000397\"\u003ECrossRef\u003C\u002Fa\u003E] [\u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov\u002Fentrez\u002Fquery.fcgi?cmd=Retrieve&amp;db=PubMed&amp;list_uids=38039286&amp;dopt=Abstract\" target=\"_blank\"\u003EMedline\u003C\u002Fa\u003E]\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003C\u002Fli\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan id=\"ref15\"\u003EAndo K, Sato M, Wakatsuki S,  et al. A comparative study of English and Japanese ChatGPT responses to anaesthesia-related medical questions. BJA Open.  Jun 2024;10:100296. [\u003Ca target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fdx.doi.org\u002F10.1016\u002Fj.bjao.2024.100296\"\u003ECrossRef\u003C\u002Fa\u003E] [\u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov\u002Fentrez\u002Fquery.fcgi?cmd=Retrieve&amp;db=PubMed&amp;list_uids=38975242&amp;dopt=Abstract\" target=\"_blank\"\u003EMedline\u003C\u002Fa\u003E]\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003C\u002Fli\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan id=\"ref16\"\u003EOpenBuddy\u002Fopenbuddy-mistral-7b-v13.1. Hugging Face.  URL: \u003Ca target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fhuggingface.co\u002FOpenBuddy\u002Fopenbuddy-mistral-7b-v13.1\"\u003Ehttps:\u002F\u002Fhuggingface.co\u002FOpenBuddy\u002Fopenbuddy-mistral-7b-v13.1\u003C\u002Fa\u003E [Accessed 2023-11-13]\n                        \u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003C\u002Fli\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan id=\"ref17\"\u003EJiang AQ, Sablayrolles A, Mensch A,  et al. Mistral 7B. arXiv.  Preprint posted online on  Oct 10, 2023.  [\u003Ca target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fdx.doi.org\u002F10.48550\u002FarXiv.2310.06825\"\u003ECrossRef\u003C\u002Fa\u003E]\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003C\u002Fli\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan id=\"ref18\"\u003Eguidance-ai\u002Fguidance: A guidance language for controlling large language models. Github.  URL: \u003Ca target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fguidance-ai\u002Fguidance\"\u003Ehttps:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fguidance-ai\u002Fguidance\u003C\u002Fa\u003E [Accessed 2023-11-13]\n                        \u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003C\u002Fli\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan id=\"ref19\"\u003ELiu X, Wu J, Shao A,  et al. Uncovering language disparity of ChatGPT on retinal vascular disease classification: cross-sectional study. J Med Internet Res.  Jan 22, 2024;26:e51926. [\u003Ca target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fdx.doi.org\u002F10.2196\u002F51926\"\u003ECrossRef\u003C\u002Fa\u003E] [\u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov\u002Fentrez\u002Fquery.fcgi?cmd=Retrieve&amp;db=PubMed&amp;list_uids=38252483&amp;dopt=Abstract\" target=\"_blank\"\u003EMedline\u003C\u002Fa\u003E]\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003C\u002Fli\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan id=\"ref20\"\u003ELiu M, Okuhara T, Chang X,  et al. Performance of ChatGPT across different versions in medical licensing examinations worldwide: systematic review and meta-analysis. J Med Internet Res.  Jul 25, 2024;26:e60807. [\u003Ca target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fdx.doi.org\u002F10.2196\u002F60807\"\u003ECrossRef\u003C\u002Fa\u003E]\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003C\u002Fli\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan id=\"ref21\"\u003EGuillen-Grima F, Guillen-Aguinaga S, Guillen-Aguinaga L,  et al. Evaluating the efficacy of ChatGPT in navigating the Spanish Medical Residency Entrance Examination (MIR): promising horizons for AI in clinical medicine. Clin Pract.  Nov 20, 2023;13(6):1460-1487. [\u003Ca target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fdx.doi.org\u002F10.3390\u002Fclinpract13060130\"\u003ECrossRef\u003C\u002Fa\u003E] [\u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov\u002Fentrez\u002Fquery.fcgi?cmd=Retrieve&amp;db=PubMed&amp;list_uids=37987431&amp;dopt=Abstract\" target=\"_blank\"\u003EMedline\u003C\u002Fa\u003E]\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003C\u002Fli\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan id=\"ref22\"\u003EPfohl SR, Cole-Lewis H, Sayres R,  et al. A toolbox for surfacing health equity harms and biases in large language models. Nat Med.  Dec 2024;30(12):3590-3600. [\u003Ca target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fdx.doi.org\u002F10.1038\u002Fs41591-024-03258-2\"\u003ECrossRef\u003C\u002Fa\u003E] [\u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov\u002Fentrez\u002Fquery.fcgi?cmd=Retrieve&amp;db=PubMed&amp;list_uids=39313595&amp;dopt=Abstract\" target=\"_blank\"\u003EMedline\u003C\u002Fa\u003E]\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003C\u002Fli\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan id=\"ref23\"\u003EOmar M, Soffer S, Agbareia R,  et al. Socio-demographic biases in medical decision-making by large language models: a large-scale multi-model analysis. Nat Med.   2025;31:1873-1881. [\u003Ca target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fdx.doi.org\u002F10.1038\u002Fs41591-025-03626-6\"\u003ECrossRef\u003C\u002Fa\u003E]\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003C\u002Fli\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan id=\"ref24\"\u003EZack T, Lehman E, Suzgun M,  et al. Assessing the potential of GPT-4 to perpetuate racial and gender biases in health care: a model evaluation study. Lancet Digital Health.  Jan 2024;6(1):e12-e22. [\u003Ca target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fdx.doi.org\u002F10.1016\u002FS2589-7500(23)00225-X\"\u003ECrossRef\u003C\u002Fa\u003E] [\u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov\u002Fentrez\u002Fquery.fcgi?cmd=Retrieve&amp;db=PubMed&amp;list_uid